Class AbstractItem

java.lang.Object
com.akmal.springfoodieappbackend.model.AbstractItem
Direct Known Subclasses:
CartItem, OrderLineItem
@MappedSuperclass public abstract class AbstractItem extends Object
The class encapsulates the behaviour of an item and extracts the common behaviour between OrderLineItem and a CartItem, to avoid duplication.
